## 👁️ Advanced Feature: Mirrorless Digital Vision (MDV)
The Raven-1 replaces traditional glass mirrors with a high-definition, low-latency digital suite.

- **360° Situational Awareness:** Integrated camera arrays feed real-time data to Aura-OS.
- **AI Contrast Optimization:** Enhanced visibility for low-light and high-glare environments.
- **Aerodynamic Gain:** Removing physical mirrors reduces drag, further optimizing the Power Reactor's efficiency.
